        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="106" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>For example, a <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ScaleTransform3D.ScaleX%2A&gt;</ph> value of 1.5 stretches an object to 150 percent of its original width.</source>
